sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant Edge as Edge Origin
    participant Raw as Raw Object Store
    participant Q as Job Queue
    participant GPU as GPU Worker
    participant Enc as Encoded Store
    participant CDN as CDN
    participant Meta as Video Metadata

    Note over C,Meta: UPLOAD + TRANSCODE
    C->>Edge: POST /upload/init
    Edge-->>C: upload_id, chunked_url
    loop chunked upload
        C->>Edge: PUT /upload/{id}/chunk
        Edge->>Raw: append bytes
        Edge-->>C: offset_acked
    end
    C->>Edge: POST /upload/{id}/finish
    Edge->>Meta: create video {status: PROCESSING}
    Edge-)Q: enqueue transcode job
    Edge-->>C: video_id

    Note over Q,Enc: TRANSCODING DAG
    Q-)GPU: split into 6s segments
    par parallel encode
        GPU->>GPU: encode 240p
    and
        GPU->>GPU: encode 720p
    and
        GPU->>GPU: encode 1080p/4K
    end
    GPU->>Enc: write HLS chunks + manifest
    GPU->>Meta: status = READY

    Note over C,CDN: PLAYBACK
    C->>Meta: GET /video/{id}
    Meta-->>C: manifest URL
    C->>CDN: GET manifest.m3u8
    CDN-->>C: variant list
    loop ABR per chunk
        C->>C: measure bandwidth
        C->>CDN: GET chunk @ chosen bitrate
        alt CDN hit
            CDN-->>C: chunk bytes
        else miss
            CDN->>Enc: fetch chunk
            Enc-->>CDN: bytes
            CDN-->>C: chunk bytes
        end
    end
